reviewText: You'll Get Interesting Sleep From It

7 min of a naked woman doing stuff, 30 sec of dialog. Repeat 10 times. During all that dialog, they establish and maintain a simple plot and the scenes keep getting hotter. Fake boobs, but there's a lot of snatch to make up for it.

If I want a good movie, I shop good movies. Likewise with the bad ones. This one falls into a rare category. Excellent soft core.
